@startuml diagrama-pacotes
title Diagrama de Pacotes — Visão lógica (MVC + persistência + bootstrap)

package "com.example" {
  class Application <<entrypoint>>

  package "aluguel.controller" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.service" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.repository" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.model" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.dto" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.security" <<Folder>> {
  }

  package "aluguel.bootstrap" <<Folder>> {
  }
}

aluguel.controller ..> aluguel.service : depende
aluguel.controller ..> aluguel.security : @Secured / papéis
aluguel.service ..> aluguel.repository : depende
aluguel.service ..> aluguel.model : usa
aluguel.service ..> aluguel.dto : usa
aluguel.repository ..> aluguel.model : persiste
aluguel.security ..> aluguel.repository : login (usuário)
aluguel.bootstrap ..> aluguel.repository : seed (dev)
aluguel.bootstrap ..> aluguel.security : hash de senha

note bottom of aluguel.controller
  Camada **Controller** (HTTP, JSON).
end note

note bottom of aluguel.service
  Camada **Service** (regras de negócio).
end note

note bottom of aluguel.repository
  **Repository** (persistência JPA).
end note

note bottom of aluguel.bootstrap
  Carga opcional de dados demo (**app.dev.seed.enabled**).
end note

@enduml
